= Configuration using pluginManagement section =

== Objectives ==

Sample project for examining the different configurations of plugins
in plugin-management. 

* When the configuration is given in the {{{plugin}}} section itself, 
  it will be used in the {{{validate}}} phase as well as during 
  invocation of {{{enforcer:enforce}}}.
* When the configuration is given in a {{{exection}}} section,
  it will be used **only** in the {{{validate}}} phase but not during 
  invocation of {{{enforcer:enforce}}} so the later one will **fail**!

